==Adjective==
'''quantitative'''
#a measurement expressed not by means of a natural language description, but rather in terms of numbers. The opposite (natural language, not descriptions measured in terms of numbers) is [[qualitative]]. For example, "She is 190 cm tall" is a quantitative description, while "She is very tall" is a quantative description.

